Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,



Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{so I spelled "Mini House" wrong all this time? ORZ}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:36.86,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Good Luck, Inokuma Yawara-san!\NOshiuri Travel Agency#
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:39.87,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Gold Medal! Yawara!\NGinza Can-Can#
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:46.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's something you don't see every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.09,0:01:49.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not so much seeing her off as fighting over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.31,0:01:54.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know one of those firms is going to get their hands on Inokuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:59.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which makes her transfer to Saikai U a non-starter, right, Mr. {\i1}All Sports News{\i0\fscx30} {\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:07.52,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not going to Saikai U, and she's not joining one of those three firms.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:18.57,epTitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord0.3\be1\pos(320,420)\3c&H3548D5&\c&H3932EE&}The Opening Act of the Yugoslavia World Championships!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:21.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll root for you from my TV set.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:23.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget our souvenirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:27.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, Fujiko-san, isn't it great that you get to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:28.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're just a training player.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:29.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:31.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:35.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:39.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was actually going to compete in the tournament, I'd be quaking with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:40.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And also,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:43.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,we have something else to look forward to, Inokuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:46.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A stopover in Singapore!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:51.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be staying overnight while we wait for our connecting flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:55.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That gives us lots of time to go shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:58.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:02.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I was going to the World Championships!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:06.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare forget our souvenirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:10.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me through! Make way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:11.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.51,0:03:12.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanazono-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:16.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're finally going, Fujiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:16.45,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:17.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:21.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But remember, I'm just a training player.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:24.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it's amazing they chose you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:28.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By comparison, I'm... I'm so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,utterly worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:35.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, we'll both go as members of the national team.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:37.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:40.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:45.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't believe they're a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:48.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how guys and girls are, Yawara-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:53.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Tsurukame Travel might be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.92,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Signs: Good Luck, Yawara-san!!\N Tsurukame Travel#
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:55.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For mercy's sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:04:00.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,why didn't you make at least one giant banner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:01.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the sizes and colors the other firms have!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:09.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, it's Inokuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:14.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma-san! Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:16.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,See? She didn't even notice us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:20.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:24.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and don't forget the Dior perfumes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:27.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking the time to see me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:31.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We wish you the best. We'll be cheering for you when you're on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:36.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it isn't much, but please accept this token.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:41.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, it's a very small token.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:45.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best and bring back the gold medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:46.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:48.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you dilly-dallying? Our flight's leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:52.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:53.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys look familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:57.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:59.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:03.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, umeboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:07.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We know you'll miss the taste of Japan while you're in Eastern Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:18.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy these. Cordial Tsurukame Travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:21.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how they tempted you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:23.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:27.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't tempt me in any way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:30.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Matsuda, I'm glad you came! Carry our luggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:33.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is making them so heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:36.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Food, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:41.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, "tempted"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:44.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.57,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:51.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, maybe I did. I was only...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:58.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. We'll talk about it later in Yugoslavia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:00.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going there on business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:03.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be talking about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:06.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be too busy with your articles anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Now wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:09.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you can it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:13.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you flappin' your gums? Shut up and carry the luggage!
