Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:27.80,Insert-English,Insert Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(200,200)}I stand there still, in the pouring rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:27.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's impossible for Yawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:30.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, really, it's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:31.69,Insert-Romaji,Insert Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(200,200)}{\kf10}{\kf29}se{\kf23}ka{\kf27}i{\kf69}juu {\kf41}i{\kf32}ki {\kf25}wo {\kf47}hi{\kf24}so{\kf22}me{\kf37}te
