Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:35.75,Insert-English,Insert Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(200,200)}as you and I see each other, eye to eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:34.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about Obayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:37.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The free-weights would be too much for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:36.89,Insert-Romaji,Insert Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(200,200)}{\kf56}Chu! {\kf53}Chu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:36.89,Insert-English,Insert Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(200,200)}Kiss! Kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:39.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about Takabe Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:47.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:57.65,Insert-Romaji,Insert Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(200,200)}{\kf19}{\kf50}da{\kf51}i{\kf26}su{\kf21}ki {\kf26}da{\kf21}t{\kf24}ta {\kf31}no
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:57.65,Insert-English,Insert Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(200,200)}I've loved him.
