Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:09:02.40,Insert-English,Insert Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(200,200)}I've always been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:03.59,Insert-Romaji,Insert Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(200,200)}{\kf19}{\kf23}se{\kf25}i{\kf47}i
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:03.59,Insert-English,Insert Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(200,200)}I showed—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:38.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiko-san, can't you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:44.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the recline function on this seat is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:46.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's switch seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:51.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. You need to rest for the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:53.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:57.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it gets too bad, let me know. I'll switch seats with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.99,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Free-Weight Class#
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:18.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a darn shame she's only a training player.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:28.06,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Free-Weight Class\N Ito Fujiko#
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:31.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:45.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This place looks kind of bleak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:50.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like Singapore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jody!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:07.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:09.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you've recovered, Jody!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:12.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Jody Rockwell-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:17.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the long-awaited reunion of two rivals? How exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:29.04,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these people... competing in the world championships?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:34.24,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so glad I'm not on the national team!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:36.92,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank goodness for that—</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:41.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:47.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:53.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:55.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:58.73,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Teleko... Teleshikova.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:00.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:46.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,slavia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:58.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And the beautiful, blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:01.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Danube!{cha-cha-chan}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:08.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiko-san, stop dancing and let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:15.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame that you won't be in the free-weight class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:16.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Jody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:19.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The free-weight and the 48kg-and-under competitions are on the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:24.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about the 48kg-and-under and just do the free-weight class!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:28.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that. The Japanese national team makes the decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:35.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not going to enter, then I'll only compete in the 72 kg heavyweight class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:41.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Teleshikova will be shocked, because she entered the free-weights just to face you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:43.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Jody-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:49.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma-san can easily handle two classes in one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:52.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Fujiko-san, you have no consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:54.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're not competing, Fujiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, and I'm happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiko-san is acting just like a tourist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:14:02.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All she does is buy gifts for her boyfriend back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:05.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma-san, you're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:08.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your husband, Jody?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:09.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always come along as your coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:12.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My darling didn't come with me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:15.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a weightlifting competition in Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:18.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm spending a lot of money making international calls to him every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:21.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm writing letters to him daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:26.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My darling eats a lot, but sadly I won't be able to serve him delicious food.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:30.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanazono-san always says my cooking is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so your boyfriend eats a lot too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:39.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Just the other day he ate 20 onigiri, snarfed 20 boiled eggs,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:43.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and drank 20 bottles of milk like it was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:47.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A man that eats a lot can never be bad. You must be in heaven, Fujiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:50.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please, Jody-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:58.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are lucky to have men.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my gosh, Inokuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:04.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you have Matsuda in your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:06.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:12.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're really seeing him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:15.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew there was something going on with you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:19.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still keeping up that act?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:22.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be a little more honest with your feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:26.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really, you two! There's nothing between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:33.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? The way he looks at you says more than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:36.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So there {\i1}was{\i0\fscx130} {\r}more to it, Inokuma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:40.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda will be coming here anyway to report on the games.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:44.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give those two a helping hand, Fujiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:48.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A new romance could start in this foreign country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:51.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Geez, there's nothing between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.21,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Not with him.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:16:00.81,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagata! Yamagata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:03.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:05.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:08.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kosaku! Are you listening, Kosaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:12.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You must come home now, Kosaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:19.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father... Your father... just suffered a cerebral hemorrhage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:25.71,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die, Dad!</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:33.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:39.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All our players are in peak form, right, Master Inokuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:43.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, have you decided who's competing in the free-weight class?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.95,0:16:47.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:52.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep looking, the one who's peaking right now should jump out at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:59.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3... 1, 2, 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:02.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara-san's techniques do stand out the most, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:03.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As they should!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:08.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You know a good thing when you see it,\N Mr. Japanese Women's Coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:11.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, why thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:15.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But doing two weight classes in one day would be too much, even for Yawara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:19.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:23.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have until the day before the free-weights to choose your player.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:24.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:29.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Master, what have you been writing all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:32.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Autographing books!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:37.53,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Writing: The Gentle Way was not Built in a Day\N Inokuma Jigoro#
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:37.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All those foreign athletes will be falling over themselves to get my autograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:43.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll even give you one. "To Yanagizawa-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:46.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:51.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And here we have "Sayzen Bach-san." Now that's a weird name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:54.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now for "Anton da Silva-san"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:02.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Inokuma-san! You're really in your groove!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:04.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it hurt, Fujiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:05.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:16.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's the first day of the tournament. Everyone must be feeling tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:21.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to do my work,\N even without Kosaku around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:26.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should've gone to Yamagata with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:30.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who will be my father-in-law is in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:34.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I must do my job here for Kosaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:36.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this shot is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:41.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take pictures without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:51.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That was scary! She's not just tense,\N she's ready to erupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:52.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:55.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I didn't say anything! Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:58.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I must find someone less scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like them! They look relaxed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:07.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Yawara-chan! How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:07.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuniko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:11.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The camerawoman from {\i1}All Sports News{\fscx30} {\r}! Good day to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:17.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:24.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kosaku didn't come, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:27.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda-san didn't come?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:31.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He never misses any of Inokuma-san's matches!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:34.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he got bored with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:36.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:41.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara-chan {\i1}has{\i0\fscx130} {\r}become quite the superstar now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:45.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kosaku gets excited and bored with things really easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:49.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad he didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:55.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inokuma-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.23,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be my chance.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:03.46,thought,,0000,0000,0000,,My chance to crush a romantic rival.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:11.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, everyone in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:16.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are at Pioneer Hall in Belgrade, Yugoslavia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:20.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the opening act of the tournament, commentator Yamashita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:23.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is. Here's hoping for a good tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:28.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be watching the semifinal match for the women's 72 kg heavyweight division.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:31.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan's Tohdoh has survived up to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:33.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she's fought hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:37.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Soviet Teleshikova is only going to compete in the free-weight class,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:42.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,which makes Canada's Jody Rockwell the favorite to win the 72 kg heavyweights.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:48.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Win this one, Tohdoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:51.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get the gold medal,\N it'll put the rest of us at ease!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:54.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Todo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:58.25,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohdoh appears to be out of shape since she's over the ideal weight,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:00.16,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,but what do you think of her up till now, Yamashita-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:05.22,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,I say she performed solidly today. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:07.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's now facing Cuba's Martinez,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:09.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,who's never appeared in an international tournament before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:12.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no data on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:14.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:23.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can hear the thud! I'm so glad I'm not playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:24.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow-Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:25.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mere a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:27.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Master Inokuma, you're hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:29.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, c'mere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:41.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He got bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:46.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even scarier up close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:48.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me one of your "un, deux, trois."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:56.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretend you're Tohdoh and you're timing your move against that Manekineko girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:22:00.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:01.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, un, deux...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:05.60,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Martinez countered Tohdoh's Osoto and got a Yuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.60,0:22:09.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! She got you just now! Try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.92,0:22:14.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now! Un, deux...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:20.69,announcer,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Martinez gets a Kosoto Gari Ippon! Tohdoh is finished! {not in the Judo Guide}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.89,0:22:24.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You big dummy! You just lost by an Ippon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:28.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be returning to Japan wearing a medal that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.54,0:22:30.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A medal?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:33.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal? Tohdoh's out already?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.86,0:22:36.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is gonna be a long tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.05,0:22:40.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kosaku didn't come. Maybe he's bored with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:45.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kosaku gets excited and bored with things really easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:47.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's bored with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:54.85,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\be1}Sign: The Barcelona Olympics in {\c&H5C74FF&}285{\r} Days#
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:22:59.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the World Championships have finally started!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:01.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you must be fit to be tied, aint'cha?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.85,0:23:02.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:06.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to get two gold medals, or best of all, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.39,0:23:09.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not getting two or three no matter how much you want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:11.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's talking about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.04,0:23:16.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we have all the familiar competitors here, let's see what's in store.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:16.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:19.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jam-Packed with International Contenders!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:24.75,nextEp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.7\b1\be1\fs30\fscy100\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HCBD9EA&\pos(450,310)}Jam-Packed with International Contenders!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:22.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get my Kosoto Gari if you don't watch!
